cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image analysis and pattern recognition. Additionally, the use of deep learning models for automated annotation further supports this categorization. The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it uses machine learning algorithms to perform automated annotation. The use of deep learning models also suggests that the paper may belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Information retrieval (cs.IR) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with the identification of specific patterns in images. Finally, multimedia (cs.MM) is a possible sub-category as the paper deals with the analysis of reflectance confocal microscopy images.
